{"tid":8664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"傳樂視欠債高達500億拖供應商過百億數","createTime":"2016-11-28T12:18:25.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-29T17:49:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36ff33a501cb0bfd181600fbec02982b0ea16574","tid":8664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:18:25.000Z","msg":"有無爸絲打既公司 比 樂視 拖緊數 <br />\n有公司..整網頁野...小數目.. 已經 遲左 3-4個月 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161108/55887556\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161108%2F55887556&d=fdRvfDoGC%2F4r2f%2BTASGWW8W%2Flfx08C7TTpsJ%2BRLLqlo%3D&h=8139699f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20161108%2F55887556&h=eeda7d58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20161108/55887556</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n 最新消息.... <br />\n1.出左律師信比佢，限定時間前都無處理到個 payment.... <br />\n2. 打左去樂視財務部 電話號碼1號 到，打左好多次, 終於通左, 但話我打錯電話...<br />\n3. 打左去樂視財務部 電話號碼2號 到，打左好多次, 仲未通....<br />\n4. 現在打緊去樂視財務部 電話號碼3號 <br />\n樂視和小米昨日在微博掀起罵戰，被外界關注樂視的財政狀況，有內地傳媒指出，樂視包括上市公司以及樂視汽車在內，已融資逾500億（人民幣‧下同），但有指已開始拖欠供應商款項，資金鏈疑似出現問題。<br />\n<br />\n目前樂視三間主要公司，內地上市的樂視網、LeEco以及樂視超級汽車，傳欠債達500億以上，當中拖欠供應商便多達100億元，主要是因為樂Pro3手機推遲發貨，被指資金鏈出現斷裂疑雲。而樂視汽車燒錢亦已超過100億元。<br />\n值得留意的是，樂視在176億貸款當中，有部分是來自董事長賈躍亭的無償私人貸款予樂視，賈躍亭自2011年起已多次減持樂視股份，但他並非個人套現資金，而是將套現所得再借款給樂視作融資，以個人資金貸款給公司，而不讓公司發債，分析指是因為樂視貸款額度已用盡，因此大股東要自掏腰包去融資給公司。"},{"pid":"3906e2e24ed3d19eea53214483cc078fdc16e702","tid":8664,"uid":3668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:21:46.000Z","msg":"Ponzi scheme <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想問下當日吹奏樂視班大陸仔去晒邊"},{"pid":"6a9dc0548fd154a5c85dfc69396ab41e8bba419d","tid":8664,"uid":2110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:22:02.000Z","msg":"估下會唔會比人收購<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b961e243bf696dc8b56611e0995674d6def89ef","tid":8664,"uid":5637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:25:23.000Z","msg":"富有中國特色的生意模式<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5f1d2140d7620fe3274c3583cbaf3073b04f77","tid":8664,"uid":33718,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:27:33.000Z","msg":"仲諗住Join佢個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3968c8416981cc5cd79a83fc208dd331766766d3","tid":8664,"uid":8441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T12:44:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>仲諗住Join佢個英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一年應該無事掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee06a61df129d6f917734d00e4b62925bc6d3970","tid":8664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:06:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f7a2996e99ab52623792eda42d48af72b13e16","tid":8664,"uid":2854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:07:43.000Z","msg":"唔使驚，橫掂支那政府會補貼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd57655d1a6cc743eb36fe9f377922a728896512","tid":8664,"uid":1778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:10:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 仲頂到幾耐"},{"pid":"7b69f3250b205a5ff7b30987f54f7b6d77b84f7f","tid":8664,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-28T16:44:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbba3a726851ae6ba1a9cdbdf